{"tid":481513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超英趕美】中國廁所設計超Open 震驚全球62億人","createTime":"2017-11-27T09:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T02:34:04.000Z","uid":88681,"like":88,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"2d23f61f9863159c01c51edb996bf31e8962b20c","tid":481513,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://imgs.gotrip.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/gt-feature-toilet_14608174825a1651c130643.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.gotrip.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2Fgt-feature-toilet_14608174825a1651c130643.jpg&h=9432492a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本電視節目《世界くらべてみたら》早前訪問了300個在日本居住的外國人，關於他們剛到日本時受到的文化衝擊，有中國人表示，兩地廁所差異非常大，主持人睇到中國廁所嘅相都嚇親！日本洗手間的清潔度也算是世界聞名，沒想到廁所也可以成為吸引遊客的地方。一於睇下到底外國人點睇中日廁所！（*題中震驚62億人是指扣除中國人人數後得出的全球人口數字。）<br />\n<br />\n<strong>中日廁所文化衝擊</strong><br />\n<br />\n在日本居住了3年的中國人接受訪問時，提到來日本之前，曾聽說過當地洗手間非常乾淨，乾淨程度是足以讓人在裡面吃便當。當時她抱著半信半疑的心態來到日本，竟然發現傳聞都是真有其事！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/-2017-11-22-6.00.53_3002935705a154d2905494.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F-2017-11-22-6.00.53_3002935705a154d2905494.png&h=953d1f60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">到日本之前，曾聽過廁所乾淨到可以在內進食的傳聞。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國式廁所⋯⋯</strong><br />\n<br />\n記者接著問她關於中國廁所的問題，她尷尬地指，中國很多廁所連門都沒有。此話一出，再配合節目組找到的圖片，讓攝影棚中的主持人和嘉賓驚叫連連。在日本住過，習慣了乾淨企理的洗手間，再看到這麼「原始」的廁所，難怪日本人和外國人都感到非常衝擊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/-2017-11-22-6.01.18_15396056135a154dc39f642.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F-2017-11-22-6.01.18_15396056135a154dc39f642.png&h=4c25ca7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被問到中國的洗手間是怎麼樣時，也只能尷尬回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/-2017-11-22-6.09.20_5514180415a154dc193f1f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F-2017-11-22-6.09.20_5514180415a154dc193f1f.png&h=3d849f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甚麼間隔都沒有的踎廁，嚇壞了一眾主持和嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/-2017-11-22-6.09.26_6816876495a154dbfd6604.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F-2017-11-22-6.09.26_6816876495a154dbfd6604.png&h=80ef1e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即使有些踎廁旁邊多了一面牆，但整體仍然是沒有門的設計，不少外國人到中國旅遊時都感到震驚。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>排排踎超嘔心</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國嘉賓更指出，原來上述廁所已經是較先進的設計，以前中國的廁所只有一條坑</span>，大家前後排踎住屙，排後面嗰個就慘啲⋯⋯嘉賓更指，她小時候曾經不小心失足跌了下去，名副其實「跌落屎坑」，嚇到渡邊直美大叫！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.weekendhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/-2017-11-22-5.43.20_9855636185a154ee0b36ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.weekendhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F-2017-11-22-5.43.20_9855636185a154ee0b36ef.png&h=33ff1283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人要用時就要前後排同時去，後面就望住前面個屁股同⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gotrip.hk/itineraryguide/japan_guide/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A/6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotrip.hk%2Fitineraryguide%2Fjapan_guide%2F%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%2589%2580-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E8%25A1%259D%25E6%2593%258A%2F6%2F&d=QZmhlYg1stwKHdqHr4jgz54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=27ec7a36\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gotrip.hk/itineraryguide/japan_guide/%E5%BB%81%E6%89%80-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A/6/</a>"},{"pid":"aacda3359e70b48d5cb3de0c8ed933d744b18b36","tid":481513,"uid":65743,"like":265,"dislike":3,"score":262,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/170312_2968fd6a1cb38cf6d1afdf9e3a376ec8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F170312_2968fd6a1cb38cf6d1afdf9e3a376ec8.jpg&h=2b22e103&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29f297ce7e1fac93b9d42667a1a71eaa1c616f13","tid":481513,"uid":2054,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:03:45.000Z","msg":"驚呆70億地球人"},{"pid":"346efedb44773ab9db6d9fbdb21b623cabcc7031","tid":481513,"uid":100150,"like":50,"dislike":4,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:04:31.000Z","msg":"支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野性之大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係支那痾屎肯定會扯曬旗獸性大發姦咗條囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f62fc85edf99deb86b3bf05091ac0ba405a325","tid":481513,"uid":5490,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:08:56.000Z","msg":"大街大行佢地都屙得啦，e d小兒科"},{"pid":"dd37d211e5eff0751159eb427d318691f63bcd1f","tid":481513,"uid":81113,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:10:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野性之大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係支那痾屎肯定會扯曬旗獸性大發姦咗條囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你入大陸d女廁痾屎？"},{"pid":"67f009d0d102658b9cc153d4570b78b444ba20c6","tid":481513,"uid":44454,"like":70,"dislike":2,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T09:12:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野性之大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係支那痾屎肯定會扯曬旗獸性大發姦咗條囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你入大陸d女廁痾屎？</blockquote><br />\n佢打錯字，應該係囝囝