22,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過北京南鑼鼓巷，叫做旅遊區。有次行過條後巷，見有厠所標誌，入去洗個手，而佢厠所個設計係好細心既，洗手盤喺門口唔使入厠所。一開始洗手就聽倒背後有人打機&hellip;&hellip;我屌&hellip;門口就有幾個踎厠&hellip;兩條大陸仔一左一右面向住我痾住屎一齊打機！望倒嗰半秒見倒條細J喺度之餘仲見倒舊屎跌落去個坑度，仆佢個街呢世都忘記唔倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難想像到大城市會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鄉鎮都有佢"},{"pid":"090230e6d5829ee4d7397cf5f7c0eb7a0de3db4f","tid":481513,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"有冇蝗討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f09e6c25aafc4d01e5e4966048239469185fad","tid":481513,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有一日係圓方入去廁所個陣<br />\n聽到個支那女人大大聲問有無踎廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6079bcfd698556d4c12ec81a54f2e9b97fff6e91","tid":481513,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f505f6fc85e2006ebf8c1bb20a167148c3e6ec5","tid":481513,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港商場厠所世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0155a195042cb203032ac1eeafe9e978e4ed56","tid":481513,"uid":120