faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有將煙頭周圍dum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204364900f08e6e2309faac8c115a21e8c3752fe","tid":481513,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來中國人咁鍾意踎, 係由細到大痾屎訓練而成的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本人都用和式踎廁架，不過人踎佢支那人又踎，踎到佢地啲人周街痾咁撚無品，真係貽笑大方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好明顯係支那低劣人種問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb89a17e8c59a88946eb72a2fbc420da403fea25","tid":481513,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公道啲講，講Open，有無見過印度首都新德里街上面嘅公廁？我淨係見過男人去，唔肯定係無女廁，定係男女共用&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n睇到嚇撚死你&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n五毛學人公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公道啲講<br />\n我淨係知非洲大把地方冇廁所<br />\n我支已經好好"},{"pid":"b063d0e1ce8abb4e8de0afa6d3591c63265297f4","tid":481513,"uid":21917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"支那即使而家d商場點靚 個wc都可以係好撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489ca96f4e3a5d4ab57d132c8b27b1c5337e7c64","tid":481513,"uid":128827,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:15:36.000Z","msg":"我有幸係強國去過咁既廁所，我將門鎖左，出面d人係咁踢門，我出黎果陣係一個人，生得高大大隻無人係我面前屌，不過就係咁細聲屌。廁所係咁樣，5個位我唔鎖門真心去唔掂"},{"pid":"eb542f9ef5f0108cc5e7034cde608c7ea90df648","tid":481513,"uid":56661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢樣中國最多只能認第二, 印度先恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote